Description: Documentation of and links to data for wordnets in 20 languages (Albanian- Arabic- Danish- English- Persian- Finnish- French- Hebrew- Italian- Japanese- Basque- Catalan- Galician- Spanish- Indonesian- Malaysian- Norwegian (Bokmal and Nynorsk)- Portuguese- Thai).  Size- quality and license varies widely- but all licenses are open licenses that allow redistribution.There is also an online search interface.
